            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "BENEFITS OF LIVING IN A BUILDING: BIG BROWN BATS (EPTESICUS FUSCUS) IN ROCKS VERSUS BUILDINGS",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Cori L.",
