            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "Roosting behaviour and roost selection of female big brown bats (Eptesicus fuscus) roosting in rock crevices in southeastern Alberta",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Cori L",
                    "lastName": "Lausen"
