            "title": "Drivers of bat roles in Neotropical seed dispersal networks: abundance is more important than functional traits",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Rafael De Souza",
                    "lastName": "Laurindo"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
